{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·002.1", "text_original": "將仲子兮，無踰我里，無折我樹杞。豈敢愛之？畏我父母。仲可懷也，父母之言，亦可畏也。", "text_normalized": "將仲子兮，無踰我里，無折我樹杞。豈敢愛之？畏我父母。仲可懷也，父母之言，亦可畏也。", "notes": "將仲子 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·002.2", "text_original": "將仲子兮，無踰我牆，無折我樹桑。豈敢愛之？畏我諸兄。仲可懷也，諸兄之言，亦可畏也。", "text_normalized": "將仲子兮，無踰我牆，無折我樹桑。豈敢愛之？畏我諸兄。仲可懷也，諸兄之言，亦可畏也。", "notes": "將仲子 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·002.3", "text_original": "將仲子兮，無踰我園，無折我樹檀。豈敢愛之？畏人之多言。仲可懷也，人之多言，亦可畏也。", "text_normalized": "將仲子兮，無踰我園，無折我樹檀。豈敢愛之？畏人之多言。仲可懷也，人之多言，亦可畏也。", "notes": "將仲子 Chinese stanza 3."}
